def dfs(n, k):
    diff = abs(n - k)
    if diff >= 2:
        if n > k:
            print('CHEF')
        else:
            print('CHEFINA')
    elif diff == 0:
        if n % 2:
            print('CHEF')
        else:
            print('CHEFINA')
    elif diff == 1:
        mini = min(n, k)
        if mini % 2:
            print('CHEF')
        else:
            print('CHEFINA')
tried = int(input())

    (n, k) = mul()
    dfs(n, k)
